Trendify

Trendify is one of my first completed frontend projects, built using only HTML and CSS.

This project was an important step in my learning journey because it was one of the first times I managed to structure a more complete website, including sections like a navbar, cards, carousel, and a footer.

Technologies Used:
HTML5
CSS3
Bootstrap

What I Practiced:

With Trendify, I started experimenting with some of the main Bootstrap components and layout features, including:

Navbar
Cards
Carousel
Footer structure
Project Notes

This is one of my earliest projects, so the code and design are still simple compared to my more recent work.
However, it represents an important stage of my growth as a frontend developer and shows how I began exploring page structure and UI components.

I’m sharing this project because it reflects the beginning of my path in web development and helps show my progress over time.